data.description: Don’t miss this beautiful home on 5.71 acres in the Lexington School district! Incredible location just outside the Village of Lexington and near the newly built Junior High and High School! Enjoy complete seclusion and privacy - the home is surrounded by woods and situated down a long and picturesque driveway. Outside is truly an oasis with a nice barn with concrete floor, electric, 4 horse stalls, workshop space and chicken coop. Fabulous pool with Amish built deck ready for enjoying that summer sunshine. Inside this move in ready home you will find generous amounts of space with 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. Primary bedroom with private bathroom. Large living room with fireplace, fresh paint, crown molding and beautiful hardwood floors. Updated kitchen with maple cabinets with built in organizers, quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Cozy family room with wood burning fireplace. Make your appointment to see this beautiful property today!!
